==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''[[hyperbolic]] [[sine]]'''

#{{mathematics}} a [[hyperbolic function]] that is written in symbol [[sinh]] and defined as the following:
:<math>\sinh(x) = \frac{e^x - e^{-x}}{2}</math>

